 is 18 years old.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.saflii.org/za/legis/num_act/nrta1996189/ |title=National Road Traffic Act, 1996 [No. 93 of 1996&#93; - G 17603 |publisher=Saflii.org |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Tanzania}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.2pass.co.uk/ages3.htm|title=Minimum Driving Ages around the World|website=www.2pass.co.uk|access-date=2016-08-14}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Tunisia}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldtravelguide.net/tunis/travel-to |title=Travel to Tunis |publisher=Worldtravelguide.net |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Zambia}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|16<ref>{{cite web |url=http://zamcom.smetoolkit.org/zambia/en/content/en/2643/Investment-Climate |title=Investment Climate &#124; SME Toolkit Zambia |publisher=Zamcom.smetoolkit.org |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150220205723/http://zamcom.smetoolkit.org/zambia/en/content/en/2643/Investment-Climate |archive-date=2015-02-20 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Zimbabwe}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|16<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aupairinamerica.com/resources/culture_quests/zimbabwe.asp |title=Au Pairs from Zimbabwe - Culture Quests |publisher=Aupairinamerica.com |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|}\n\n== Americas ==\n=== North America ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=\"100\" | State\n! width=\"130\" | Minimum driving age\n! width=\"300\" | Notes\n|-\n| {{flag|Canada}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|16 in most provinces (Graduated Licensing Program)<BR/>14 with GLP in [[Alberta]]<ref>https://www.alberta.ca/class-7-learners-licence.aspx#toc-0</ref><BR/>15 with GLP in [[Yukon]], [[Northwest Territories|NWT]], and [[Nunavut]] <ref>https://yukon.ca/en/driving-and-transportation/driver-licensing/get-drivers-licence#find-out-if-youre-eligible</ref><ref>https://www.yd.com/drivers-license-nunavut<