ta}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.transport.gov.mt/land-transport/driving |title=TM Portal - General Info on Driving in Malta |publisher=Transport.gov.mt |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012185452/http://www.transport.gov.mt/land-transport/driving |archive-date=2018-10-12 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Netherlands}} \n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 17 for cars<br/>16 for mopeds and tractors<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rijksoverheid.nl/onderwerpen/rijbewijs/vraag-en-antwoord/voor-welke-soorten-bromfietsen-heb-ik-een-bromfietsrijbewijs-brommerrijbewijs-nodig |language=Dutch |title=What license do I need a moped, scooter, scooter or moped car to drive? |accessdate=15 October 2016}}</ref>\n| {{see also|Driving licence in the Netherlands}}Driving age for cars is 17 with supervision.<br>Driving lessons available at 16\u00bd.<br>Unrestricted licence available at 18.\n|-\n| {{flag|Norway}}\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|18 for cars<br>16 for mopeds and light motorcycles\n| {{see also|Driving licence in Norway}}\n|-\n| {{flag|Poland}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18{{citation needed|date=July 2016}}\n| {{see also|Driving licence in Poland}}\n|-\n| {{flag|Portugal}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18 for cars\n\n16 for motorcycles{{citation needed|date=July 2016}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Romania}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<br/>16 for motorcycles up to 125&nbsp;cc<ref>{{cite web|url=https://europa.eu/youreurope/citizens/vehicles/driving-licence/get-driving-licence/romania/index_ro.htm |title=Optaining a driver's licence in UE-Romania |accessdate=2 January 2019 | language=romanian}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Slovakia}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|17{{citation needed|date=July 2016}}\n| Driving age for cars is 17 with supervision.<br>Unrestricted licence available at 18.\n|-\n| {{flag|Slovenia}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|16 for cars and motorcycles{{citation needed|date=July 2016}}\n| Driving age for cars is 16 with supervision.<br>Unrestricted licence available at 18.\n|-\n| {{flag|Spain}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|15 for mopeds and quads<br /> 16 for motorcycles up to 125&nbsp;cc <br /> 18 for general license<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sede.dgt.gob.es/es/tramites-y-multas/permiso-de-conduccion/obtencion-permiso-licencia-conduccion/clases-permiso-conduccion-edad.shtml |title=Driving age Spain |accessdate=May 10, 2018 | language=spanish }}</ref>\n\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Sweden}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18 for cars<ref name=\"transportstyrelsen.se\">https://www.transportstyrelsen.se/globalassets/global/publikationer/vag/korkort/tran-092--allt_om_korkort_en_webb.pdf</ref><br/>15/16 for mopeds and tractors\n| {{see also|Driving licence in Sweden}}Driving age for cars is 16 with supervision.<br>Unrestricted licence available at 18.<ref name=\"transportstyrelsen.se\"/>\n|-\n| {{flag|Switzerland}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18 for cars, 14 for mopeds and tractors<ref>{{cite web|url=https://driving-instructor.fahrlehrervergleich.ch/categories.php |title=Driver\u2019s license categories in Switzerland |accessdate=September 6, 2018}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|United Kingdom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|17 (cars)\n16 (mopeds and tractors)(card of disabled and in receipt of PIP <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/Motoring/DriverLicensing/WhatCanYouDriveAndYourObligations/DG_4022547 |title=Vehicles you can drive - GOV.UK |publisher=Direct.gov.uk |date=2015-01-16 |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n| {{see also|Driving licence in the United Kingdom}}\n|}\n\n=== Rest of Europe ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=\"100\" | State\n! width=\"130\" | Minimum driving age\n! width=\"300\" | Notes\n|-\n| {{flag|Albania}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18{{citation needed|date=October 2015}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Andorra}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alltravelandorra.com/Andorra/Car_Ren