occo.php |title=Morocco Driving Guide |publisher=Economy Car Hire |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.your-morocco-tour.com/about-morocco |title=About Morocco |publisher=Your-morocco-tour.com |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n|\n|- \n| {{flag|Mozambique}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18{{citation needed|date=July 2016}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Namibia}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aupairinamerica.com/resources/culture_quests/namibia.asp |title=Au Pairs from Namibia - Culture Quests |publisher=Aupairinamerica.com |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Niger}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{cite web|author=Avando Systems Ltd |url=http://www.travcour.com/g_page.php?pageid=689&Pagetitle=Niger |title=Niger visa service UK, London|publisher=Travcour.com |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Nigeria}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18{{citation needed|date=July 2016}}\n|\n|-\n| ''{{flag|R\u00e9union}}'' (France)\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18{{citation needed|date=July 2016}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Senegal}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18{{citation needed|date=July 2016}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|South Africa}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|17\n| The National Road Traffic act specifies that a driver needs to be 17 to legally obtain a license for all motor vehicles under 3500&nbsp;kg. 17 years old may allow one to obtain a learners license, to drive while supervised by an already licensed driver who has had their license for more than a year. Yet to obtain an actual drivers license, the age is 18 years old.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.saflii.org/za/legis/num_act/nrta1996189/ |title=National Road Traffic Act, 1996 [No. 93 of 1996&#93; - G 17603 |publisher=Saflii.org |date= |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Tanzania}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.2pass.co.uk/ages3.htm|title=Minimum Driving Ages around the World|website=