/publikationer/vag/korkort/tran-092--allt_om_korkort_en_webb.pdf</ref><br/>15/16 for mopeds and tractors\n| {{see also|Driving licence in Sweden}}Driving age for cars is 16 with supervision.<br>Unrestricted licence available at 18.<ref name=\"transportstyrelsen.se\"/>\n|-\n| {{flag|Switzerland}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18 for cars, 14 for mopeds and tractors<ref>{{cite web|url=https://driving-instructor.fahrlehrervergleich.ch/categories.php |title=Driver\u2019s license categories in Switzerland |accessdate=September 6, 2018}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|United Kingdom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|17 (cars)\n16 (mopeds and tractors)(card of disabled and in receipt of PIP <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/Motoring/DriverLicensing/WhatCanYouDriveAndYourObligations/DG_4022547 |title=Vehicles you can drive - GOV.UK |publisher=Direct.gov.uk |date=2015-01-16 |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n| {{see also|Driving licence in the United Kingdom}}\n|}\n\n=== Rest of Europe ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! width=\"100\" | State\n! width=\"130\" | Minimum driving age\n! width=\"300\" | Notes\n|-\n| {{flag|Albania}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18{{citation needed|date=October 2015}}\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Andorra}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.alltravelandorra.com/Andorra/Car_Rental/Driving_Tips.htm#8 |title=Driving Tips for Andorra |accessdate=August 25, 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100409150846/http://www.alltravelandorra.com/Andorra/Car_Rental/Driving_Tips.htm |archivedate=April 9, 2010 }}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Armenia}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rac.co.uk/driving-abroad/armenia/ |title=Driving in Armenia |publisher=RAC |date=2013-01-10 |accessdate=2015-02-20}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| {{flag|Azerbaijan}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|18<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.apa.az/news.php?id=124827 |title=Minimum driving age changed in Azerbaijan |acces